confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596163036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657981441/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596163036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657981662\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657981441\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"0c73c1f8-7d19-47b0-89b7-3252e7f48696\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596163036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596163036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/Tutorials/razorback-whiptail/sourceimages_Original_Textures.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596163036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657981441/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596163036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657981662\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657981441\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"0c73c1f8-7d19-47b0-89b7-3252e7f48696\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596163036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596163036&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>For some time now, I've been eager to learn how to use Mari software. When <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kurtisdawe\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kurtis Dawe</a> offered several artists the opportunity to work on one of his assets, I immediately seized the chance. Being passionate about creatures and monsters since my introduction to 3D work, I enthusiastically immersed myself in this exciting project. </p><p>Access to such a high-quality asset enabled me to focus on practicing the main areas I wanted to refine: creature texturing and look-dev.</p><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/657162498/RazorBack+Modeling\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657162498\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"razor_refs_thumb.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/razor_refs_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762598161734&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657981441/razor_refs_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762598161734&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"656834815\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"razor_refs_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657981441\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"407d62c0-e43b-4f73-9882-ca9fc05d3384\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/razor_refs_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762598161734&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/razor_refs_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1762598161734&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RazorBackWhiptail-Modeling\"><span data-colorid=\"u8a87e3u