chment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"razor_comp_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657981441\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"8314d3bb-7b17-45ea-be15-bcad06629896\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/razor_comp_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598796656&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/razor_comp_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598796656&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RazorBackWhiptail-Compositing\"><span data-colorid=\"wbge8trrz5\">Compositing</span></h1><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"RazorBackWhiptail-AbouttheArtists\">About the Artists</h3></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image-20251108-104755.png\" width=\"201\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/image-20251108-104755.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598882018&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=202\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657981441/image-20251108-104755.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598882018&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"357\" data-width=\"355\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657260874\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image-20251108-104755.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657981441\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"10a08140-6eb5-4886-9d3a-921d8388b580\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/image-20251108-104755.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598882018&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=402&amp;height=404 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/image-20251108-104755.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598882018&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=202 1x\" /></span><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.artstation.com/matteollorens\" rel=\"nofollow\">Matteo Llorens</a></p><p>Matteo is a student who just graduated from ESMA and is passionate about the world of film, especially creatures. He is currently looking for a job as a creature artist in the VFX industry and makes a living from his passion!</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image-20251108-104809.png\" width=\"201\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/image-20251108-104809.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598895864&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=205\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657981441/image-20251108-104809.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598895864&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"356\" data-width=\"349\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657555673\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image-20251108-104809.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657981441\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"ef1fb54f-04e3-4faf-909c-f16d3d5dfca2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/image-20251108-104809.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598895864&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=402&amp;height=410 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657981441/image-20251108-104809.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762598895864&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=201&amp;height=205 1x\" /></span><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kurtisdawe\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kurtis Dawe</a></p><p>Kurtis works as a Senior Artist at ILM / Disney Studios Sydney and over the years he has created some of the most memorable characters and creatures for the entertainment industry, including The Lion King, Godzilla, and Marvel Films.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><hr /><p>This project is available with an Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License. This allows you to share and redistribute for non-commercial purposes, provided that you credit the original author.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"3fafb653-5776-4e40-ba90-88d6f95b3574\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-inform